# Release-build env (NODE_ENV=production). Loaded by `expo export:embed` during
# `./gradlew assembleRelease`. `npm run android` bundles in development mode and
# never reads this file, so local dev keeps using .env (127.0.0.1). Process env
# (apk:staging/apk:dist via cross-env) still overrides — @expo/env never
# overrides a var already present in process.env. EXPO_PUBLIC_* (client-public) only.
